                                    <button class="btn text-decoration-none text-info" type="button">
                                        How is animation as a career?
                                    </button>
                                     <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14 fa-lg text-white ml-auto mr-3" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fa" data-icon="plus" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa fa-plus fa-lg text-white ml-auto mr-3"></i> -->
