                                    <div class="card-body">
								 	    <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p class="text-white">Animation can be a rewarding and fulfilling career for individuals who have a passion for storytelling, creativity, and visual arts. You have<b> diverse Opportunities, there is a global demand, you can use creative expression and work in a collaborative environment.</b></p>
