                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p class="text-white">There are a variety of options for those who want to get into the field of animation like animator, storyboard artist, character designer, 3D modeller, texture artist, rigging artist, lighting artist, visual effects artist, compositing artist, motion graphic designer, art director, producer, animation director, educator, independent artist and much more.</p>
