                                <div id="job_body_3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="job_posting_3" data-parent="#accordion3">
                                    <div class="card-body">
								 	    <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>Animators with less than three years of experience might earn an average annual salary ranging from INR 2,00,000 to INR 4,00,000. Senior animators with more than five years of experience can earn higher salaries, typically ranging from INR 8,00,000 to INR 15,00,000 or more annually.</p>
                                                <div class="brdr-0 brdr-left-lightblue  fs-14 p-2">

                                                </div>
