                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>We offer a wide range of courses with experienced instructors. We also have a fantastic support team and make sure every student is reaching his/her ultimate potential. The academy is affiliated with various universities and organisations, including the Savitri Bai Phule Pune University and the Sandip University, Nashik. The courses offered by the academy would be designed to equip students with the necessary skills and knowledge to work in the animation and media industries.</p>
