			 <div class="container">
				  <!--<div class="blur"></div>-->
				      <!--What is VFX ?-->
                    <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-12 ">
                        <div class="accordion" id="accordion10">
                            <!-- Card 3 -->
                            <div class="brdr-none p-2 bxsh-1 brdr-1">
                                <div class="card-header brdr-none p-2 brdr-2 bxsh-1  d-flex align-items-center " id="job_card_10" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#job_body_10" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="job_body_10">
                                    <button class="btn text-decoration-none text-info" type="button">
                                       How is VFX as a career?
                                    </button>
                                     <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14 fa-lg ml-auto mr-3 text-white" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fa" data-icon="plus" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa fa-plus fa-lg ml-auto mr-3 text-white"></i> -->
                                </div> <!-- .card-header -->
                                <div id="job_body_10" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="job_posting_10" data-parent="#accordion10">
                                    <div class="card-body">
								 	    <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>Overall, a career in VFX can be fulfilling for those who enjoy combining artistic <b>creativity with technical skills. You have a scope for Creativity and Innovation, there are a lot of Technological Advancements hence promoting global demand, you have job variety and work-life balance.</b></p>
                                                <div class="brdr-0 brdr-left-lightblue  fs-14 p-2">

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div> <!-- #job_type_3 -->
                            </div> <!-- .card -->
                        </div><!-- #accordion3 -->
                    </div><!-- End of Job Column 2 --> 
                    <!-- What is the difference between hollywood VFX and bollywood VFX  ? -->
                    <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-12">
                        <div class="accordion" id="accordion11">
                            <!-- Card 3 -->
                            <div class="brdr-none p-2 bxsh-1 brdr-1">
                                <div class="card-header brdr-none p-2 brdr-2 bxsh-1  d-flex align-items-center " id="job_card_11" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#job_body_11" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="job_body_11">
                                    <button class="btn text-decoration-none text-info" type="button">
                                       	What kind of jobs are offered after the VFX course?
                                    </button>
                                    <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-plus fa-w-14 fa-lg ml-auto mr-3 text-white" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fa" data-icon="plus" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa fa-plus fa-lg ml-auto mr-3 text-white"></i> -->
                                    
                                </div> 
                                <div id="job_body_11" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="job_posting_11" data-parent="#accordion11">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>After completing a VFX course, individuals can pursue various job opportunities like <b>VFX Artist/Compositor, 3D Modeller/Animator, Texture/ rigging Artist, Texture Artist, FX Artist (Special Effects), Match move Artist, Technical Director, VFX Supervisor, Colour Grading Artist, Previsualization Artist and much more.</b></p>
                                                <div class=" brdr-0 brdr-left-lightblue  fs-14 p-2 h-auto">

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div> <!-- #job_type_4 -->
