                                <div id="job_body_25" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="job_posting_25" data-parent="#accordion25">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>Motion graphics is a form of visual communication that combines graphic design elements with animation to create dynamic, engaging, and visually appealing content. It involves the use of animated graphic elements, text, and imagery to convey information, tell a story, or enhance the visual experience in various media formats.</p>
                                                <div class=" brdr-0 brdr-left-lightblue  fs-14 p-2 h-auto">
