                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 text-white">
                                                <p>The average salary for Editor is ₹52,000 per month in India. Those with less than three years of experience may earn an average annual salary ranging from INR 2,00,000 to INR 4,00,000. Senior editors with more than five years of experience may earn higher salaries, typically ranging from INR 8,00,000 to INR 15,00,000 or more annually.</p>
